tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AlgorithmPerformance (
    algorithm_id int PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255),
    performance_metric VARCHAR(255),
    index_used BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE Index_Statistics (
    index_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    index_name VARCHAR(100),
    index_size BIGINT,
    last_updated_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Query_Logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    query_text TEXT,
    execution_time FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
CREATE TABLE AlgorithmPerformance (algorithm_id INT PRIMARY KEY, algorithm_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, execution_time FLOAT NOT NULL, performance_rating INT)

CREATE TABLE index_usage (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    index_name VARCHAR(255),
    index_type VARCHAR(50),
    index_columns TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE index_statistics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    index_id INT,
    total_operations INT,
    total_time FLOAT,
    efficiency_rating FLOAT
);
